  <wpt lon="141.1528104543686" lat="43.07643821753684">
    <name>Yama-no-Ie Hut</name>
    <sym>Dot</sym>
    <type>Dot</type>
    <desc>Unlocked year-round, in the winter there is fuel (coal) that can be used for heating. Pots, pans, mattresses available for use.

Officially, all visitors should book in advance at Hokkaido University. Fee for staying is 80yen per night (yes, 80yen). More details here: http://www.14degrees.org/hokkaido-ski-touring-mt-okuteine-yama-no-ie-hut-and-mt-tsuge-sapporo-japan/</desc>
    <cmt>Unlocked year-round, in the winter there is fuel (coal) that can be used for heating. Pots, pans, mattresses available for use.

Officially, all visitors should book in advance at Hokkaido University. Fee for staying is 80yen per night (yes, 80yen). More details here: http://www.14degrees.org/hokkaido-ski-touring-mt-okuteine-yama-no-ie-hut-and-mt-tsuge-sapporo-japan/</cmt>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lon="141.15323" lat="43.08739200000001">
    <name>Mt. Okuteine summit</name>
    <sym>Dot</sym>
    <type>Dot</type>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lon="141.15236520767212" lat="43.07541942431622">
    <name>Utopia Ski Run</name>
    <sym>Dot</sym>
    <type>Dot</type>
    <desc>This is a good clear ski run, directly southwest of the hut.</desc>
    <cmt>This is a good clear ski run, directly southwest of the hut.</cmt>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lon="141.13116633445907" lat="43.067105882535884">
    <name>Mt. Tsuge summit</name>
    <sym>Dot</sym>
    <type>Dot</type>
    <desc>Nice summit with fantastic views across to Jozankei.</desc>
    <cmt>Nice summit with fantastic views across to Jozankei.</cmt>
  </wpt>
